  "text": "Proof. Fix a meridian m. By definition, the curve f \u2212i j (m) is in the kernel of the representation \u03c1 i j for all i j . On the other hand, the sequence (f \u2212i j (m)) converges to\u03bb in PML(S). This implies that\u03bb is not realized; see for instance [CITATION_1] Section 4] .",
